                <ab xml:lang="gez">
                ወገጹ፡ ዘፍጹም፡ በጽልመት፡ ፈርሃ፡ ወደንገጸ፡ ዲያብሎስ፡ ርእዮ፡
                ብሁተ፡ ልደት፡ በሥጋ፡ አምላክ፡ በሥጋ፡ በሲኦል፡ 
                በዝ፡ ቃል፡ አድኅና፡ ለአመትከ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/>
                </ab>
            </div>
            <div type="translation">
                <note>Tentative translation by <persName ref="JK"/>.</note>
                <ab>
                    And the face of (?) the Perfect One in the darkness –
                    the Devil feared and was afraid,
                    when he saw the Only-Begotten One in the flesh, God in the flesh in Sheol.
                Through this word (<foreign xml:lang="gez">qāl</foreign>), save the soul of your maidservant <gap reason="ellipsis"/>
                </ab>
            </div>
